						               													<description>Citytrip Antwerp is the second game in the Citytrip series featuring new gameplay elements.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As a tour guide you want to create the most memorable trip by visiting famous buildings and musea, events, restaurants and more.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Citytrip Antwerp is a flip &amp;amp; write game that is quick to setup and easy to play. With a basic and advanced scoresheet, 23 starting points and 44 different missions, no 2 games will feel the same!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;One player flips the upper card of the action stack. Simultaneously everybody chooses 2 actions that are horizontally or vertically adjacent (=7 possible combinations). Each player creates a road and circles achieved goals which give points on the scoresheet. The game ends after 15 turns. The player with the highest satisfaction score wins Citytrip Antwerp.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
